## Step 5：推荐话术

### 主话术（今天发）

> Amit, I owe you an apology.
>
> I promised you the information "by tomorrow morning" on May 5th, and it took me until May 11th to get back to you. That's not the standard of service you deserve — especially for a brand owner who shared detailed specifications, logo files, and packaging references with us. No excuses, just a commitment: from here on, you'll have my direct attention.
>
> To make it easier for you, here's what I suggest:
>
> **Size split for 500 pcs**: 90cm(150) / 100cm(200) / 110cm(150). Based on Amazon baby category data, 100cm is typically the best-selling size. Adjust if needed.
>
> **Logo method**: Woven label (sewn-in). It's more premium, washable, and suits Kinjolluxe's "premium luxury" positioning better than heat transfer.
>
> **Shipping**: I'm checking the door-to-door (DDP) option to Uttarakhand 249407 right now so you don't have to handle customs clearance. The DAP quote ($191, 7-9 days) is the baseline, and I'll have the DDP figure for you within 24 hours.
>
> I'm also preparing an initial design mockup for the packaging box based on your navy blue/maroon/gold color scheme — I'll share it as soon as it's ready, no commitment needed.
>
> One more thing: you mentioned period panties and seamless women's underwear. While those aren't in our production line, I can ask my network if there's a reliable factory I can connect you with. Would that help?
>
> Let's get this moving. What do you think about the size split and woven label?

### 话术设计思路

| 要素 | 体现 |
|------|------|
| **道歉** | 第一句直接道歉，不找借口 |
| **降门槛** | 给出默认尺码分配+推荐logo方式，客户只需要说yes/no |
| **补漏洞** | DDP门到门运费正在查，主动解决清关问题 |
| **超额交付** | 准备免费mockup，用行动补偿等待时间 |
| **关系破局** | 主动offer帮客户找女性内衣供应商 — 即使不是我们的生意，建立信任 |
| **具体推进行** | 最后落到一个简单的确认点 |

